    <article id="main-content" class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="What is the Volant Station?" class="article-title">
          What is the Volant Station?
          
        </h1>

        <div class="article-author">
          
          <div class="article-meta">
            

            <div class="meta-group">
              
                <span class="meta-data"><time datetime="2025-12-09T16:43:14Z" title="2025-12-09T16:43:14Z" data-datetime="relative">December 09, 2025 16:43</time></span>
                <span class="meta-data">Updated</span>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        
          <div class="article-subscribe"><div data-helper="subscribe" data-json="{&quot;item&quot;:&quot;article&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;/hc/en-us/articles/47210125869203-What-is-the-Volant-Station/subscription.json&quot;,&quot;follow_label&quot;:&quot;Follow&quot;,&quot;unfollow_label&quot;:&quot;Unfollow&quot;,&quot;following_label&quot;:&quot;Following&quot;,&quot;can_subscribe&quot;:true,&quot;is_subscribed&quot;:false}"></div></div>
        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><h3 id="h_01KC1ZXA085PQMZRVFB5TV5CF4" data-start="339" data-end="402">Explore, Fly, Fight, and Race at the Heart of MUD Territory</h3><p data-start="404" data-end="651"><strong data-start="404" data-end="422">Volant Station</strong> is the <strong data-start="430" data-end="475">central multiplayer hub and starting zone</strong> for the MUD faction in the Star Atlas UE5 game, available on the <strong data-start="541" data-end="561">Epic Games Store</strong></p><p data-start="404" data-end="651"><strong data-start="541" data-end="561"><img class="wysiwyg-image-resized hs-image-align-none" style="aspect-ratio: 688/436; height: auto; width: 688px;" src="https://20489070.fs1.hubspotusercontent-na1.net/hubfs/20489070/image.png" alt="image" width="688" height="436"></strong></p><h3 id="h_01KC1ZXA08VD0KTQVW9NT5CQ07" data-start="404" data-end="651">&nbsp;</h3><h3 data-start="404" data-end="651" id="h_01KC1ZXR3GBPPFH4V4DX2E2A31">What Can You Do in Volant Station?</h3><p data-start="701" data-end="790">Volant Station offers multiple gameplay activities for both solo and multiplayer players:</p><ul data-start="792" data-end="1273"><li data-start="792" data-end="893" data-list-item-id="e11d29bdd71868cf6614cc4b1e760a272"><p data-start="794" data-end="893"><strong data-start="794" data-end="813">Explore Freely:</strong> Navigate the station and surrounding platforms on foot or using a <strong data-start="880" data-end="891">jetpack</strong></p></li><li data-start="894" data-end="970" data-list-item-id="e0ca857a460fa582f67333b7f1442fcb1"><p data-start="896" data-end="970"><strong data-start="896" data-end="913">Summon Ships:</strong> Spawn your owned ships at designated pads and take off</p></li><li data-start="971" data-end="1041" data-list-item-id="edef15e02fb6e87ceb945e340cb100113"><p data-start="973" data-end="1041"><strong data-start="973" data-end="982">Race:</strong> Compete on the racetrack solo or in multiplayer sessions</p></li><li data-start="1210" data-end="1273" data-list-item-id="ed18364ce81d822bb6f848a6a8b0f222a"><p data-start="1212" data-end="1273"><strong data-start="1212" data-end="1235">Meet Other Players:</strong> Socialize in open multiplayer lobbies</p></li></ul><h3 id="h_01KC1ZXA08ZC9SGDG9T0HNGZS8">&nbsp;</h3><h3 id="h_01KC1ZXR3GX9TTC8SK8XD6C2D4">Jetpack Mobility</h3><p data-start="1304" data-end="1560">All players are equipped with a <strong data-start="1336" data-end="1352">free jetpack</strong> by default, allowing vertical movement and easier exploration across the Volant Station environment. Mastering this is especially helpful for reaching hidden areas or gaining a tactical edge in combat zones.</p><h3 id="h_01KC1ZXA08K9CYMVWPY1YJTMQM">&nbsp;</h3><h3 id="h_01KC1ZXR3G8E44VAYJZA4E51RM">Lore&nbsp;</h3><p data-start="1598" data-end="1846">Volant Station is the <strong data-start="1620" data-end="1656">MUD faction’s central stronghold</strong>, orbiting above their territory in the Galia Expanse. It's a strategic outpost for exploration, research, and fleet deployment and now a hub for training the next generation of explorers</p></div>

          

          
        </div>
      </section>

